Umthombo weSolezwe ongathandanga ukudalulwa uthe kusolwa impi yezigodi ngokubulawa kwalaba ababaili njengoba kuthiwa kumaqembu asemapulazini akule ndawo alwayo. Isolezwe lithole ukuthi amadoda amathathu ebezihlalele emotweni iToyota Hilux ngabo-9 ebusuku ngesikhathi kugasela amadoda angaziwa evulela ngenhlamvu ebhekise kulawa akade ekwiHilux. Kushone amadoda amabili, angeke aze adalulwe amagama awo ngoba imindeni yawo ibingakazikhombi izidumbu okuthiwa abekade ekwiHilux kwathi eyodwa yaphuthunyiswa esibhedlela isesimeni esibi. ULt Colonel Thulani Zwane wamaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal usiqinisekisile isigameko sokudutshulwa kwamadoda eColenso. Uthe amaphoyisa aseColenso aphenya amacala amabili okubulala nelilodwa lokuzama ukubulala. Uthe ayaziwa imbangela yokudutshulwa kwala madoda ngoba wuphenyo lwamaphoyisa oluzoveza ukuthi bekwenzenjani. Kwesinye isigameko amaphoyisa ophiko lwezokutshuza kuMasipala weTheku aphuthume e-Albert Falls lapho kushayisane khona izikebhe ngoKhisimusi. Kuye kwaminza abantu ababili. USnr Supt Parboo Sewpersad okhulumela amaphoyisa kaMasipala weTheku uthe amaphoyisa abo atshuzayo asebenzisana nakahulumeni (SAPS) ukucinga abaminzile e-Albert Falls. “Sithole isidumbu somuntu oyedwa ngoKhisimusi, izolo siye saqala phansi ukutshuza kodwa amaphoyisa ethu nakahulumeni awazange amthole omunye. Bazomthungatha nakusasa (namhlanje) ngokuthi batshuze,” kusho uSewpersad.